data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvider
data.value: select T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.ROLE_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.WORK_PHONE_NUMBER, T1.WORK_FAX_NUMBER, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.WORK_FAX_AREA_CD, T1.WORK_PHONE_EXT, T1.WORK_PHONE_AREA_CD, T1.LOC_CONT_FOR_IRS, T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.REASON_CODE, T3.CREATED_BY, T3.CREATED_DTSTAMP, T4.TYPE_CODE, T4.NAME, T4.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 join CKT_OFFICE T4 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T1 on (T4.OFFICE_ID = T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID = @spdGeneratedId1) join CKT_OFC_SRCPRV_RLT T3 on (T1.ROLE_CODE = T3.OSP_R_ROLE_CODE) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T3.OSP_R_EFFECTIVE_DT) and (T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T3.OFF_R_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T3.SPD_R_GENERATED_ID) on (T2.ROLE_CODE = T3.OSP_ROLE_CODE) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T3.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE) and (T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.OFFICE_ID = T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID = @spdGeneratedId2)

data.name: ReadOfficeServiceProviderServiceProviderOffice
data.value: select T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T1.ROLE_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T2.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T2.LAST_UPDATD_TSTAMP, T2.USER_ID, T2.LAST_NAME, T2.FIRST_NAME, T2.MIDDLE_INITIAL, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.TYPE_CODE, T3.NAME, T3.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T3 join CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T1 on (T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T1.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = @servicePrvderId) and (T1.ROLE_CODE = @roleCode) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) on T3.OFFICE_ID = T1.OFF_GENERATED_ID order by T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE

data.name: ReadServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPDATD_TSTAMP, USER_ID, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, MIDDLE_INITIAL, ROLE_CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER where SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = @servicePrvderId

data.name: ReadServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvRelationship
data.value: select distinct T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATD_TSTAMP, T1.USER_ID, T1.LAST_NAME, T1.FIRST_NAME, T1.MIDDLE_INITIAL, T1.ROLE_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.OSP_ROLE_CODE, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T2.OSP_R_EFFECTIVE_DT, T2.OSP_R_ROLE_CODE, T2.OFF_R_GENERATED_ID, T2.SPD_R_GENERATED_ID, T2.REASON_CODE, T2.CREATED_BY, T2.CREATED_DTSTAMP, T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T4 join CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T3 on (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.LAST_NAME >= @lastName) and (T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) join CKT_OFC_SRCPRV_RLT T2 on (T3.ROLE_CODE = T2.OSP_ROLE_CODE) and (T3.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T2.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE) and (T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) on (T4.ROLE_CODE = T2.OSP_R_ROLE_CODE) and (T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T2.OSP_R_EFFECTIVE_DT) and (T4.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T2.OFF_R_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T2.SPD_R_GENERATED_ID) and (@spdGeneratedId = T4.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and ( T4.ROLE_CODE in ('SS', 'AT', 'PM', 'TR') ) and (T4.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate) and (T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @discontinueDate) order by T1.LAST_NAME, T2.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvider1
data.value: select top(1) T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID, T1.LAST_NAME, T1.FIRST_NAME, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.WORK_PHONE_NUMBER, T2.WORK_FAX_NUMBER, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.WORK_FAX_AREA_CD, T2.WORK_PHONE_EXT, T2.WORK_PHONE_AREA_CD, T2.LOC_CONT_FOR_IRS from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 on (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = @servicePrvderId) and (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (@offGeneratedId = T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.ROLE_CODE = @roleCode) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate)

data.name: ReadServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvider2
data.value: select top(1) T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID, T1.LAST_NAME, T1.FIRST_NAME, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.WORK_PHONE_NUMBER, T2.WORK_FAX_NUMBER, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.WORK_FAX_AREA_CD, T2.WORK_PHONE_EXT, T2.WORK_PHONE_AREA_CD, T2.LOC_CONT_FOR_IRS from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 on (T1.USER_ID = @userId) and (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and ( T2.ROLE_CODE in ('SS', 'AT', 'PM', 'TR') ) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate) order by T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadServiceProviderOfficeServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvRelationship
data.value: select T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID, T1.LAST_NAME, T1.FIRST_NAME, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE, T3.OSP_ROLE_CODE, T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID, T3.REASON_CODE, T3.CREATED_BY, T3.CREATED_DTSTAMP, T4.OFFICE_ID, T4.TYPE_CODE, T4.NAME, T4.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T4, CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 join CKT_OFC_SRCPRV_RLT T3 on (T2.ROLE_CODE = T3.OSP_R_ROLE_CODE) and (T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T3.OSP_R_EFFECTIVE_DT) and (T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T3.OFF_R_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T3.SPD_R_GENERATED_ID) and (@ospRoleCode = T3.OSP_ROLE_CODE) and (@ospEffectiveDate = T3.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE) and (@offGeneratedId = T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (@spdGeneratedId = T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID) on (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID <> @servicePrvderId) where T4.OFFICE_ID = @offGeneratedId

data.name: ReadServiceProviderServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvider
data.value: select top(1) T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.LAST_UPDATD_TSTAMP, T1.USER_ID, T1.LAST_NAME, T1.FIRST_NAME, T1.MIDDLE_INITIAL, T1.ROLE_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T2.USER_ID, T2.LAST_NAME, T2.FIRST_NAME, T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T3.ROLE_CODE, T3.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T3.WORK_PHONE_NUMBER, T3.WORK_FAX_NUMBER, T3.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T3.WORK_FAX_AREA_CD, T3.WORK_PHONE_EXT, T3.WORK_PHONE_AREA_CD, T3.LOC_CONT_FOR_IRS, T4.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T4.ROLE_CODE, T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T4.DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T2 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T3 join CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T4 on (T1.USER_ID = @userId) and (T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T4.SPD_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T4.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) join CKT_OFC_SRCPRV_RLT T5 on (T4.ROLE_CODE = T5.OSP_ROLE_CODE) and (T4.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T5.OSP_EFFECTIVE_DATE) and (T4.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T5.OFF_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T5.SPD_GENERATED_ID) on (T3.ROLE_CODE = T5.OSP_R_ROLE_CODE) and (T3.EFFECTIVE_DATE = T5.OSP_R_EFFECTIVE_DT) and (T3.OFF_GENERATED_ID = T5.OFF_R_GENERATED_ID) and (T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID = T5.SPD_R_GENERATED_ID) on T2.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T3.SPD_GENERATED_ID
